name: Safavieh_Dane_Charcoal_Grey_Full_Size_Headboard
reviews: We got this headboard for my almost 3 year olds bed, and it's a great size for a kids room. It's not rock hard sturdy, but it's plenty sturdy. I found the color in the picture to be really accurate. Grey is the dominate color with brown tones and the piping is taupe. The legs of the headboard are metal and it's about 23 3/4 inches from the floor to the bottom of the headboard.
I decided to put this headboard in the nursery and it's perfect!! Great quality, accurate color and well made.
description: Bring a touch of sophistication into your bedroom with this headboard from Safavieh. Made with plywood, this headboard is sturdy, stable and durable. The padding provides extra comfort and support, and the linen upholstery is strong, soft and has a plush look.Available in charcoal gray to complement a range of linens and furnishingsMade of plywood and linen blend fabric for durability and softnessMeasures 54.5"H x 55.5"W x 3.7"DShips in one boxStyleTransitionalMaterialFabric, Linen, WoodTypeUpholsteredFinishGrey FinishAssemblyAssembly RequiredColorGreyFurniture PatternSolid
